        p Your Application Requires Attention
      
      .content
        p Dear #{businessOwnerName},
        
        p Thank you for submitting your business application for <strong>#{businessName}</strong>. After careful review, we need some additional information or corrections before we can approve your application.
        
        .warning
          p <strong>Admin Feedback:</strong>
          p #{adminNotes}
        
        p <strong>What's Next:</strong>
        ul
          li Review the feedback above carefully
          li Update your business information as needed
          li Resubmit your application for review
          li Our team will review your updated application within 2-3 business days
        
        p <strong>Business Details:</strong>
        ul
          li <strong>Business Name:</strong> #{businessName}
          li <strong>Category:</strong> #{businessCategory}
          li <strong>Review Date:</strong> #{reviewedDate}
        
        p Don't worry - this is a common part of the approval process. Most applications are approved after addressing the initial feedback.
        
        p If you have any questions about the feedback, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
        
        p Best regards,<br>
          The Urban Lens Team
      
